cording to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0633\u064e\u0644\u0652\u0645\u064e\u0627\u0646 \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":25976,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2018\/02\/26\/prophet-ate-fill-with-guests\/","url_meta":{"origin":26004,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Food: The Prophet only ate his fill with guests","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"February 26, 2018","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas ibn Malik reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, never combined a dish of his with meat and bread for lunch, nor for dinner, unless he was eating with a gathering of people. Source: Musnad Ah\u0323mad 13859 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Arna'ut \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0646\u064e\u0633\u0650\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":26026,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2018\/03\/05\/abu-jafar-gluttony-full-belly\/","url_meta":{"origin":26004,"position":3},"title":"Abu Ja\u2019far on Gluttony: If stomach is full, body will sin","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 5, 2018","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Abi Dunya reported: Abu Ja\u2019far, may Allah have mercy on him, said, \u201cWhen the belly is full, the body will transgress.\u201d Source: al-Ju\u0304\u2019 li-Ibn Abi\u0304 Dunya\u0304 23 \u0639\u0646 \u0627\u0628\u0646 \u0623\u0628\u064a \u062f\u0646\u064a\u0627 \